name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On August 17, a recording of Coco Lee talking about the unfair treatment she encountered when participating in "The Voice of China" was exposed online. In the recording, Coco Lee said: "Because of the Voice, I like this program. I think these young people are full of youth and love music. Our common language is love for music. I don't care about sacrificing myself. I didn't expect that they were all a bunch of bad people who wanted to mess with me because I told the truth." "I don't want to die, I just want to help these children. I said the competition system is unfair, and the program team said that the competition system is like this, and no mentor can change it."
